name: JAMBO
description: Jambo Exchange (JAMBO) is a meme-driven parody project on NEAR that presents itself as the “2nd centralized DEX.” It intentionally imitates TradFi-style custody and manual settlements as satire, not as a functional exchange. The JAMBO token was launched on meme.cooking and serves purely as a community-driven meme asset. It has no guaranteed utility or value, and users should treat it strictly as entertainment.
